<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>حذف محصول</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #b92b27, #1565c0);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .card {
            background: #191919;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            width: 400px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

            .card h1 {
                color: white;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .card .text-muted {
                color: #c1c1c1;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .card input[type="submit"] {
                border: 0;
                background: #e74c3c;
                display: block;
                margin: 20px auto;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                width: 50%;
                color: white;
                border-radius: 24px;
                transition: 0.25s;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

                .card input[type="submit"]:hover {
                    background-color: #c0392b;
                }

        .cancel-button {
            border: 0;
            background: #7f8c8d;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.25s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

            .cancel-button:hover {
                background-color: #95a5a6;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <h1>حذف محصول</h1>
            <p class="text-muted">آیا مطمئن هستید که می‌خواهید این محصول را حذف کنید؟</p>
            <p>نام محصول: @Model.Name</p>
            <p>قیمت: @Model.Price</p>
            <p>شناسه دسته‌بندی: @Model.CategoryId</p>

            <form id="Form" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="DeleteProduct" method="post">
                <input type="hidden" name="id" value="@Model.Id">
                <input type="submit" value="حذف">
            </form>
            <a href="@Url.Action("Index", "Product")" class="cancel-button">لغو</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

